datasource_id: Apple Inc. stock rises Thursday, still underperforms market@MarketWatch@2023-06-15 14:54:34.470124@Apple
data:
Shares of Apple Inc. AAPL advanced 1.12% to $186.01 Thursday, on what proved to be an all-around positive trading session for the stock market, with the NASDAQ Composite Index COMP rising 1.15% to 13,782.82 and the Dow Jones Industrial Average DJIA rising 1.26% to 34,408.06.
This was the stock's second consecutive day of gains.
